OL,3,CFamilies in fight for law change to
OL,4,Cget essential care for loved ones
OL,6,FFamilies in Northern Ireland are
OL,7,Fcalling for a change to the law to
OL,8,Fallow carers to carry out essential
OL,9,Fnursing or medial tasks.
OL,11,FLast month UTV told the stories of
OL,12,Fseveral families who have been
OL,13,Finformed by health trusts that carers
OL,14,Fpaid for by direct payments can no
OL,15,Flonger carry out
OL,17,Fthose essential tasks leaving them
OL,18,Fwith no respite.
