OL,3,CFamilies in fight for law change to
OL,4,Cget essential care for loved ones
OL,6,FThey are now calling on the health
OL,7,Fminister to act, with one petition
OL,8,Freaching almost 1,500 signatures.
OL,10,FEllie Henry is 22 years old and lives
OL,11,Fwith multiple complex conditions and
OL,12,Fneeds 24 hour care.
OL,14,FHer mother Tracey says that her
OL,16,Fcarers paid for by direct payments
OL,17,Fgave her the only break she could
OL,19,Fget. That loss has been devastating
OL,20,Ffor her and led to her starting the
OL,21,Fpetition for the change in the law.
