OL,3,CFamilies in fight for law change to
OL,4,Cget essential care for loved ones
OL,6,FClaire Hinphey son Liam has dravet
OL,7,Fsyndrome and suffers frequent seizures
OL,8,Fand needs two adults with him at all
OL,9,Ftimes. She supports the call for the
OL,10,Fchange in legislation.
OL,12,F"I'm just trying to fight for what we
OL,13,Fneed, the support we need, the support
OL,14,Fmy son needs," she said.
OL,16,FThe Department of Health said it is
OL,17,Faware there are variances in the broad
OL,18,Frange of "important tasks undertaken
OL,19,Fby personal assistants/carers under
OL,20,Fdirect payments".
