OL,6,F"The department has not issued any
OL,7,Fdirection to HSC Trusts regarding the
OL,8,Fdelegation of nursing tasks within
OL,9,Fdirect payments legislation.
OL,11,F"The department will engage with HSC
OL,12,FTrust colleagues to further clarify
OL,13,Ftheir approach regarding these
OL,14,Fmatters, to inform further action
OL,15,Frequired."
